issue.body:
The following function `f` is taken from GCC bugzilla.
https://gcc.gnu.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=111957

```cpp
int f(int a)
{
  if (a)
  return a > 0 ? a : -a;
  return 0;
}

int g(int a)
{
  return a > 0 ? a : -a;
}
```

